-- Latvia Increases 2012 Economic-Growth Forecast to 4 Percent
-- B y   A a r o n   E g l i t i s
-- 2012-07-03T13:15:05Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-03/latvia-increases-2012-economic-growth-forecast-to-4-percent.html
Latvia increased its 2012 economic-
growth forecast to 4 percent from an earlier 2 percent estimate,
citing higher-than-expected tax revenue.  The economy will expand 3.7 percent next year and 4 percent
in 2014 and in 2015, the  Finance Ministry , based in the capital,
Riga, said today in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Aaron Eglitis in Riga at 
 aeglitis@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Balazs Penz at 
 bpenz@bloomberg.net  